flowchart TD
    Start([Data Migration Start]) --> Extract[Extract Data from COBOL System]
    Extract --> Validate1[Validate Source Data]
    Validate1 --> Transform[Transform Data Format]
    Transform --> Map[Map to Target Schema]
    Map --> Clean[Data Cleansing]
    Clean --> Validate2[Validate Transformed Data]
    Validate2 --> Load[Load to Java System]
    Load --> Verify[Verify Data Integrity]
    Verify --> Compare{Data Matches?}
    Compare -->|No| Investigate[Investigate Differences]
    Investigate --> Fix[Fix Data Issues]
    Fix --> Transform
    Compare -->|Yes| Sync[Synchronize During Migration]
    Sync --> Monitor[Monitor Data Sync]
    Monitor --> Complete([Migration Complete])
    
    Extract -.-> Backup[Backup Original Data]
    Backup -.-> Archive[Archive Backup]
    
